acdecom.WaveGuide.get_domainvalues¶

WaveGuide.get_domainvalues(self)¶

Returns the characteristic properties of the waveguide and the medium.

Returns

The characteristic properties {“density”, “dynamic_viscosity”, “specific_heat”, “heat_capacity”, “thermal_conductivity”, “speed_of_sound”, “Mach_number”, “radius”, “bulk-viscosity”} of the waveguide and the medium.

Return type

dict
